          "groupId": "sql-help",
          "title": "How should I start SQL if I already know Python?",
          "author": "Isha",
          "initials": "IS",
          "timestamp": "3h ago",
          "body": "I am comfortable with Python logic, but SQL feels like a different mental model. Looking for the most useful entry path.",
          "replyCount": 10,
